content: Good game but the £ currency when you get to 186 £20 is missing to complete the level making it impossible to complete the game apart from that it's a good game kindly fix that level.

I was charged 3 times and the app doesn't let me install it on my phone... its a Samsung galaxy s10... should work but it doesn't. It looked like a great way to kids to learn the coins and bills but when tried to buy the full version started the problems...
Great app for learning money. Love it.
